      "version": 1727,
      "versionNonce": 1778331014,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774286957533,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) Use on-device location services to record user GPS coorsinates\n2) Record this evenet data locally in memory buffer \n3) To prevent Loss in device shutdown or batter depletion , periodically persisit\nthis to device's local storage ~10 seconds\n    - for eg: android : room database for largr or sharedPrefernces for smaller\namounts\n4) Send accumulated data to our server in single request or in chunks or implement\nbackgrouns sync mecahnism\n5) Upon confiramtion from remote database, clear on device local storage\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Use on-device location services to record user GPS coorsinates\n2) Record this evenet data locally in memory buffer \n3) To prevent Loss in device shutdown or batter depletion , periodically persisit this to device's local storage ~10 seconds\n    - for eg: android : room database for largr or sharedPrefernces for smaller amounts\n4) Send accumulated data to our server in single request or in chunks or implement backgrouns sync mecahnism\n5) Upon confiramtion from remote database, clear on device local storage\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HLoIw_ROmTPt05WovUG1A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1743.6169775195924,
      "y": 2866.5542827662553,
      "width": 412.8544006347656,
      "height": 28.66497737123835,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#6741d9",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 130679814,
      "version": 807,
      "versionNonce": 1214918618,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774287094828,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5.2) Handle !0M concurrent activities",
      "fontSize": 22.93198189699068,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5.2) Handle !0M concurrent activities",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "636BB30DXoQSZ88QskS68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1663.318664334221,
      "y": 3870.002382363754,
      "width": 610.740966796875,
      "height": 28.147235036915834,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#6741d9",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 797589446,
      "version": 1059,
      "versionNonce": 1156993456,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774349265451,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "5.3) Support realtime sharing of activities with freinds ",
      "fontSize": 22.517788029532667,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "5.3) Support realtime sharing of activities with freinds ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WIK3PwciQ-MRXf4owD_lg",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1684.1829124768237,
      "y": 3940.435254286854,
      "width": 835.7341488613621,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1960554118,
      "version": 2478,
      "versionNonce": 1335925680,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774349265451,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Websockets or SSE and using pub-sub to brodcast updates to friends is overkill\n- Simple polling is ideal \n    - Updates are predictable like every 2-5 seonds\n    - Real time precision isn't crictical \n- Implement smart buffering system - Intentional lag displaying location data by one\nor two update intervals ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Websockets or SSE and using pub-sub to brodcast updates to friends is overkill\n- Simple polling is ideal \n    - Updates are predictable like every 2-5 seonds\n    - Real time precision isn't crictical \n- Implement smart buffering system - Intentional lag displaying location data by one or two update intervals ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6oprbPH_Fh2vf3B3jpfCM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1752.3864271397117,
      "y": 2965.71880203271,
      "width": 835.7341488613621,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 566778800,
      "version": 2949,
      "versionNonce": 1230474672,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774349234342,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Assuming 100M DAU -> 100M new activities/day -> 36500M or 36.5B activities in a\nyear \n- Storage: 100Bytes/activity, Route: average 30m and GPS co-ordinate every 3 sec\n-> 1000/3 -> 600 points/activity (8 + 8+ 8) bytes => lat + long + timestamp *600\n~15KB * 36.5B = 547.5TB of data each year\n\n\n- Shard by time that activity was completed \n- Data Tier : hot data (recenet ones) in redis, warm data (2-12 months old)\npostgres and cold data (>1 year ~ s3)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Assuming 100M DAU -> 100M new activities/day -> 36500M or 36.5B activities in a year \n- Storage: 100Bytes/activity, Route: average 30m and GPS co-ordinate every 3 sec\n-> 1000/3 -> 600 points/activity (8 + 8+ 8) bytes => lat + long + timestamp *600 ~15KB * 36.5B = 547.5TB of data each year\n\n\n- Shard by time that activity was completed \n- Data Tier : hot data (recenet ones) in redis, warm data (2-12 months old) postgres and cold data (>1 year ~ s3)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
